00:23:37.333 --> 00:23:39.043
Ti ostaješ na svojoj strani.

00:23:39.085 --> 00:23:41.085
<i>On ostaje na svojoj.</i>

00:23:41.212 --> 00:23:43.172
Tu je.

00:23:43.214 --> 00:23:45.214
Tko je tu?

00:23:45.842 --> 00:23:47.842
Olly.

