00:26:44.687 --> 00:26:46.021
Zašto?

00:26:46.063 --> 00:26:48.063
Očito ne znaš plivati.

00:26:48.524 --> 00:26:50.234
Da, imaš pravo.

00:26:50.276 --> 00:26:52.610
Ali voljela bih pokušati.

00:26:53.946 --> 00:26:55.946
Poštujem ocean.

00:26:56.032 --> 00:27:00.118
