Znači, valjda se vidimo tada.

00:30:36.543 --> 00:30:38.587
<i>U redu. Vidimo
se tada, Maddy.</i>

00:30:38.629 --> 00:30:40.046
Okej, bok, Olly.

00:30:40.088 --> 00:30:42.088
<i>Bok.</i>

00:30:44.843 --> 00:30:47.596
<i>Ne znam kako smo se Carla i
ja uspjele tako pobrkati.</i>

