Ne.

00:32:37.748 --> 00:32:38.915
<i>Jamice?</i>

00:32:38.957 --> 00:32:40.542
Nemam jamice!

00:32:40.584 --> 00:32:41.793
Kosu.

00:32:41.835 --> 00:32:43.003
Prijatelji!

00:32:43.045 --> 00:32:45.045
Elipsa.

